name: AttributeParseTest
description: Unit tests for parsing attributes in HTML elements using Jsoup.

test_cases.name: parsesRoughAttributeString
test_cases.description: Tests the parsing of a rough attribute string in an HTML element.

test_cases.name: handlesNewLinesAndReturns
test_cases.description: Tests the handling of new lines and returns in attribute values.

test_cases.name: parsesEmptyString
test_cases.description: Tests the parsing of an empty attribute string in an HTML element.

test_cases.name: canStartWithEq
test_cases.description: Tests the parsing of an attribute that starts with an equal sign.

test_cases.name: strictAttributeUnescapes
test_cases.description: Tests the unescaping of attributes in strict mode.

test_cases.name: moreAttributeUnescapes
test_cases.description: Tests the unescaping of more complex attribute values.

test_cases.name: parsesBooleanAttributes
test_cases.description: Tests the parsing of boolean attributes in an HTML element.

test_cases.name: dropsSlashFromAttributeName
test_cases.description: Tests the dropping of a slash from the attribute name in an HTML element.
